author: max
name: Ping
install_msg:
Thanks for installing. This cog is an hidden cog, therefore no support given.
i'll recommend you 3 public ping cogs that still is supported to use: <https://github.com/Kreusada/Kreusada-Cogs>, <https://github.com/phenom4n4n/phen-cogs> or <https://github.com/Vexed01/Vex-Cogs>.

Loading this cog will remove the core's ping command and replaced with this one. On unload you will have the core one back.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
